const content = "[tcs_review_nav]\n\n\n\n<section class=\"tcs-section tcs-section--deep-navy\" style=\"text-align:left;\"> <div class=\"tcs-container\"> <!-- H1 + INTRO --> <h1 class=\"tcs-review-heading\"> Savaspin Casino Review &amp; Bonus Terms Explained </h1> <p class=\"tcs-review-intro\"> Savaspin is an online casino offering a balanced mix of bonuses, standard payment limits and responsive customer support. Based on our internal audit using the TopCasinoScout scoring framework, Savaspin achieves a <strong>TCS Score of 7,750 / 10,000</strong>. <br><br> This review is based entirely on our internal scoring table, including licensing data, bonus rules, withdrawal limits and live support testing. </p> <!-- HERO SECTION --> <div class=\"tcs-review-hero\"> <div class=\"tcs-review-hero-main\"> <div class=\"tcs-review-hero-topline\"> TopCasinoScout Score \u2022 Savaspin Casino </div> <div class=\"tcs-review-hero-row\" style=\"align-items:flex-start;\"> <!-- Left --> <div class=\"tcs-review-hero-left\" style=\"flex:1;\"> <div class=\"tcs-review-logo-circle\"> <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/192x192.webp\" alt=\"Savaspin Casino logo\"> </div> <div class=\"tcs-review-title\" style=\"flex:1;\"> <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 6px;\">Savaspin Casino</h2> <!-- STAR RATING --> <div class=\"tcs-rating\" style=\"margin:0; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap;\"> <div class=\"tcs-stars\" style=\"--tcs-fill:77.5%;\" aria-label=\"3.9 out of 5 stars\"> <div class=\"tcs-stars-base\"> <span>\u2605</span><span>\u2605</span><span>\u2605</span><span>\u2605</span><span>\u2605</span> </div> <div class=\"tcs-stars-fill\"> <span>\u2605</span><span>\u2605</span><span>\u2605</span><span>\u2605</span><span>\u2605</span> </div> </div> <div class=\"tcs-rating-text\"> 3.9 / 5.0 rating (TCS 7,750) </div> </div> </div> </div> <!-- Right --> <div class=\"tcs-review-badge-wrap\" style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-end;gap:6px;margin-top:-6px;\"> <div class=\"tcs-score-pill\"> <div class=\"tcs-score-pill-label\">TCS Score</div> <div class=\"tcs-score-pill-value\">7,750 / 10,000</div> </div> <div class=\"tcs-mini-key\"> Our TCS score evaluates bonus rules, payout limits,<br> licensing tier, support quality and risk factors. </div> </div> </div> <!-- BONUS LINE --> <div class=\"tcs-hero-bonus-line\"> <strong>Welcome bonus:</strong> New players can receive a matched bonus where the total playable balance may reach <strong>up to \u20ac2,000</strong>, depending on the initial deposit and applicable bonus crediting rules (terms &amp; wagering requirements apply). </div> <div class=\"tcs-hero-ctas\"> <a class=\"tcs-btn-primary\" href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"> Visit Savaspin Casino </a> <a class=\"tcs-btn-secondary\" href=\"/casino-rankings\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"> View Casino Rankings </a> </div> </div> <!-- MEDIA --> <div class=\"tcs-review-hero-media\"> <div class=\"tcs-review-hero-media-inner\"> <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/480x360.webp\" alt=\"Savaspin casino promotion banner\"> </div> </div> </div> <!-- MAIN GRID --> <div class=\"tcs-review-grid\"> <!-- LEFT --> <div> <div class=\"tcs-review-block\"> <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Snapshot \u2022 Pros &amp; Cons</span> <h2>Is Savaspin Casino Worth Playing?</h2> <p> According to our scoring table, Savaspin shows solid overall performance with particularly strong results in support responsiveness and bonus clarity. </p> <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:20px;\"> <div> <h3>Pros</h3> <ul> <li>Clearly defined bonus caps and wagering rules.</li> <li>Responsive live chat support during testing.</li> <li>Withdrawal limits in line with mid-tier casinos.</li> <li>Transparent communication on payments and bonuses.</li> </ul> </div> <div> <h3>Cons</h3> <ul> <li>Operates under a Tier-3 licence rather than Tier-1 regulation.</li> <li>Bonuses still require wagering before withdrawal.</li> <li>Responsible gambling tools are limited compared to top regulators.</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> <div class=\"tcs-review-block\"> <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Bonuses</span> <h2>Savaspin Welcome Bonus Explained</h2> <p> Based on internal audit notes, Savaspin offers a matched deposit bonus structure where eligible players may reach a combined playable balance of up to <strong>\u20ac2,000</strong>. </p> <p> The credited amount depends on the initial deposit size and current promotion rules. All bonus funds must be wagered before withdrawals are permitted. </p> </div> </div> <!-- RIGHT --> <div> <div class=\"tcs-review-block\"> <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Banking</span> <h2>Payments &amp; Withdrawal Limits</h2> <p> According to the scoring data, Savaspin applies standard withdrawal limits typical for offshore casinos. </p> <ul> <li>Observed withdrawal limit: <strong>around \u20ac1,000 per transaction</strong>.</li> <li>Bonus-related winnings may be subject to additional caps.</li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"tcs-review-block\"> <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Safety</span> <h2>Licensing &amp; Security</h2> <p> Savaspin operates under a <strong>Tier-3 gaming licence</strong>. While this offers basic regulatory oversight, it does not match the protections provided by Tier-1 regulators. </p> </div> <div class=\"tcs-review-block\"> <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Support</span> <h2>Customer Support Quality</h2> <p> Live chat support was tested directly. Responses were received within approximately <strong>30 seconds</strong>, with clear and consistent answers regarding bonuses and withdrawal limits. </p> </div> <div class=\"tcs-review-block tcs-verdict-box\"> <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">TopCasinoScout Verdict</span> <h2>Final Verdict on Savaspin Casino</h2> <p class=\"tcs-verdict-highlight\"> With a <strong>TCS Score of 7,750 / 10,000</strong>, Savaspin ranks as a <strong>solid mid-tier casino</strong> offering clear bonus terms and reliable support. </p> <p> It is best suited for players who value transparent conditions and responsive assistance over top-tier regulation. As always, bonuses should be used responsibly and with full awareness of wagering rules. </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section>\n\n\n\n<!-- RIGHT: TEXT + BUTTONS -->\n<div class=\"tcs-bottom-links-content\">\n  <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">More From TopCasinoScout</span>\n  <h2 class=\"tcs-bottom-links-title\">Helpful Guides &amp; Tools for 1win Players</h2>\n\n  <p class=\"tcs-bottom-links-text\">\n    Explore more expert tools, guides and rankings from TopCasinoScout to help you compare casinos,\n    understand our scoring system, avoid blacklisted sites, and play with confidence.\n  </p>\n\n  <div class=\"tcs-bottom-links-buttons\">\n    <!-- BUTTON 1: Homepage -->\n    <a class=\"tcs-btn-primary\"\n       href=\"/\"\n       target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n      Return to TopCasinoScout Homepage\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- BUTTON 2: Top Casino Bonuses -->\n    <a class=\"tcs-btn-secondary\"\n       href=\"/top-casino-bonuses\"\n       target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n      Compare Top Casino Bonuses\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- BUTTON 3: How We Rate -->\n    <a class=\"tcs-btn-secondary\"\n       href=\"/how-we-rate\"\n       target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n      Learn How We Rate Casinos\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- BUTTON 4: Blacklisted & Unsafe Casinos -->\n    <a class=\"tcs-btn-secondary\"\n       href=\"/blacklisted-and-unsafe-casinos\"\n       target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n      View Blacklisted &amp; Unsafe Casinos\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- BUTTON 5: Insider Articles / Blog -->\n    <a class=\"tcs-btn-secondary\"\n       href=\"/insider-articles/\"\n       target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n      Read Insider Articles &amp; Guides\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- BUTTON 6: Responsible gambling -->\n    <a class=\"tcs-btn-secondary\"\n       href=\"/responsible-gambling\"\n       target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n      Responsible Gambling Resources\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- BUTTON 7: Review guidelines -->\n    <a class=\"tcs-btn-secondary\"\n       href=\"/casino-review-guidelines\"\n       target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n      Casino Review Guidelines\n    </a>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  /* Make hero + main grid use the same column widths */\n  .tcs-review-hero {\n    margin: 26px 0 40px;\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: minmax(0,1.5fr) minmax(0,1.1fr);\n    gap: 26px;\n    align-items: stretch;\n  }\n\n  .tcs-review-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: minmax(0,1.5fr) minmax(0,1.1fr);\n    gap: 32px;\n    margin-top: 16px;\n  }\n\n  /* Bottom links panel */\n  .tcs-bottom-links-panel {\n    margin-top: 24px;\n  }\n\n  .tcs-bottom-links-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: minmax(0,1.1fr) minmax(0,1.4fr);\n    gap: 26px;\n    align-items: center;\n    background: #080826;\n    border-radius: 18px;\n    border: 1px solid #241e67;\n    padding: 26px 24px 24px;\n    box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(0,0,0,.45);\n  }\n\n  .tcs-bottom-links-media {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n  }\n\n  .tcs-bottom-links-media-inner {\n    width: 100%;\n    border-radius: 16px;\n    border: 1px dashed #3b348f;\n    background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #141445, #05051b);\n    padding: 12px;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n\n  .tcs-bottom-links-media-inner img {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    object-fit: cover;\n    display: block;\n  }\n\n  .tcs-bottom-links-title {\n    margin: 8px 0 10px;\n    font-size: 1.25rem;\n    color: #ffcc33;\n  }\n\n  .tcs-bottom-links-text {\n    margin: 0 0 16px;\n    font-size: .95rem;\n    color: #c9d4ff;\n    max-width: 750px;\n  }\n\n  .tcs-bottom-links-buttons {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    gap: 12px;\n  }\n\n  .tcs-bottom-links-buttons .tcs-btn-primary,\n  .tcs-bottom-links-buttons .tcs-btn-secondary {\n    font-size: .9rem;\n    padding: 9px 18px;\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 900px) {\n    .tcs-review-hero {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n    .tcs-review-hero-media {\n      order: -1;\n    }\n\n    .tcs-review-grid {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n\n    .tcs-bottom-links-grid {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n    .tcs-bottom-links-media {\n      order: -1; /* image on top for mobile */\n    }\n  }\n</style>";
